{"tid":1818664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實真心唔明點解中國人會覺得台灣係佢地國家一部分","createTime":"2020-01-10T05:54:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T07:14:01.000Z","uid":39491,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b084d74d5905aa3e778508a15604b40fd76cb6eb","tid":1818664,"uid":39491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T05:54:23.000Z","msg":"香港都叫做實際條件上係被殖民緊<br />\n有駐守摺被軍 又痴住格離 雙方法律條文又有寫（先唔講有冇正當性先）<br />\n<br />\n但台灣又對面岸 又有自己軍隊 又有得投票選總統<br />\n點解會一方面講得出要武統台灣 一方面又話係一部分 唔會好矛盾咩<br />\n<br />\n小粉紅究竟係真心覺得如果同一個國家而台灣人有得選總統而佢地冇 呢件事係冇問題 定係佢地只係唔敢面對事實 點係純粹網上監管下大家唔敢講真話"},{"pid":"dec20b9d5ca97001f2deab5e4cb25a06ecc67725","tid":1818664,"uid":91558,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T05:56:53.000Z","msg":"有邏輯思維既人就唔會信共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1ba53095ffac154b8f090f5c43d232bd386ea16","tid":1818664,"uid":58335,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T05:57:52.000Z","msg":"小粉紅：全世界都是支那的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cc28d9bd9cf17e5025b7375438073391a84c87b","tid":1818664,"uid":19978,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T05:58:33.000Z","msg":"台灣算<br />\n<br />\n咁咩朝鮮、日本都算<br />\n<br />\n以前統治過就當自己<br />\n<br />\n咁要計埋亞歷山大攻入嘅歐洲"},{"pid":"667a49bb9936274d700be4c267ef855cfe4dbe13","tid":1818664,"uid":46500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T05:59:21.000Z","msg":"因為個洗腦機關日日都係咁講"},{"pid":"fe7b2cb650648c13efe40584615e2f4a8bfad079","tid":1818664,"uid":180124,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T05:59:37.000Z","msg":"佢地覺得黃皮膚黑頭髮就理所當然係中國既<br />\n台灣係中國係天經地義既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"782bf0bdd758456f5adedba34f1b5792f77264cf","tid":1818664,"uid":272580,"l